OL,3,CMums forced to travel 13 times further
OL,4,Cto give birth as maternity unit closes
OL,6,FSome mums-to-be living in and around
OL,7,FBridgend are being forced to travel
OL,8,Falmost 13 times further to give birth
OL,9,Fas their local maternity unit closes
OL,10,Ffor refurbishment.
OL,12,FMaternity services at the Princess of
OL,13,FWales Hospital will be out of bounds
OL,14,Ffor three months from September as the
OL,15,Fhealth board makes "urgent and
OL,16,Fessential" improvements.
