OL,3,CMums forced to travel 13 times further
OL,4,Cto give birth as maternity unit closes
OL,6,FFamilies are being offered alternative
OL,7,Fcare at Prince Charles Hospital in
OL,8,FMerthyr Tydfil, 38 miles away,
OL,9,FSingleton Hospital in Swansea, 25
OL,10,Fmiles away, or the University Hospital
OL,11,Fof Wales in Cardiff, which is 20 miles
OL,12,Faway.
OL,14,FFor Jess Edwards, who has been told
OL,15,Fshe may need to have a caesarean at
OL,16,FPrince Charles Hospital, it means
OL,17,Ftravelling almost 13 times further.
