OL,6,F"That's a worry because I've got a
OL,7,Fdaughter, I have to consider where I'm
OL,8,Fsending her if we have to go down
OL,9,Fthere," she said.
OL,11,F"It's not fair for family if they
OL,12,Fwanted to come down because it's
OL,13,Fnormal isn't it for family to come and
OL,14,Fsee a newborn baby. I just don't think
OL,15,Fit's fair, it's a lot of travelling."
OL,17,FDue to give birth in October, the 37-
OL,18,Fyear-old, who has a nine-year-old
OL,19,Fdaughter, says she is already feeling
OL,20,Fworried about the pregnancy due to her
OL,21,Fage.
