OL,3,CMums forced to travel 13 times further
OL,4,Cto give birth as maternity unit closes
OL,6,F"I'm already more anxious this time
OL,7,Fhaving a baby because I'm older and
OL,8,FI'm aware of more things, whereas
OL,9,Fbefore it was quite smooth-sailing
OL,10,Fwith my daughter," she said.
OL,12,F"I feel like there's a lot more
OL,13,Fpressure now and worry. I'm already
OL,14,Ftrying to enjoy the pregnancy and not
OL,15,Fworry about it too much, so it's just
OL,16,Fcaused a bit more anxiety than I
OL,17,Fwould've wanted.
