OL,6,F"The thought of having to go somewhere
OL,7,Fwhere I've no idea what it's like
OL,8,Fthere and the distance - I don't
OL,9,Fdrive, my husband drives so it's up to
OL,10,Fhim to take me wherever I need to go -
OL,11,Fit's just made me a bit anxious, I
OL,12,Fguess.
OL,14,F"Closing the whole thing for a
OL,15,Frefurbishment just seems a bit crazy
OL,16,Fto me."
