OL,3,CMums forced to travel 13 times further
OL,4,Cto give birth as maternity unit closes
OL,6,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,7,FBoard announced the temporary closure
OL,8,Fin June for a #1million refurbishment
OL,9,Fof the hospital's air handling systems
OL,10,Fand electrical supply.
OL,12,FIt said it has been working closely
OL,13,Fwith families to ensure they are able
OL,14,Fto choose a suitable alternative.
OL,16,FIt has also said transport to hospital
OL,17,Ffor those who need it will be
OL,18,Fsupported by the Welsh Ambulance
OL,19,FService.
