OL,4,Cto give birth as maternity unit closes
OL,6,FThose who are not expecting a
OL,7,Fcomplicated pregnancy are encouraged
OL,8,Fto consider giving birth at Royal
OL,9,FGlamorgan Hospital's midwife-led unit
OL,10,Fin Llantrisant.
OL,12,FThe closure comes after inspectors
OL,13,Ffound "concerning" staffing levels at
OL,14,Fthe maternity unit at Singleton
OL,15,FHospital in Swansea, with some mums
OL,16,Ffacing delays in getting pain relief.
